            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Cartula de Castellare. In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi Dei eterni. Anno
                        dominice incarnationis millesimo centesimo vicesimo quinto, quarto Xo
                        kalendas februarii, indictione tertia. Manifestus sum ego <persName
                            key="#Viscount" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/104"
                            >Rogerius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomes</rs> filius bone memorie
                            <persName>Ildibrandi</persName> quia pro Dei amore et salute anime mee
                        meorumque remedium parentum, sicut <persName key="#Count"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/96">Ildebrandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> filius <persName key="#Count"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/97">Rainerii <rs key="#Count"
                                >comitis</rs>, qui Malabranca fuit vocatus</persName>, in me
                        commisit et dedit et <rs key="#Littera/mandatum">tradidit potestatem</rs>,
                        ut ego pro se et in vice sua et per me ipsum facerem securitates et
                        obbligationes et refutationes in <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/78">Sancti Quirici
                        </orgName>de <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/86"
                            >Populonio</placeName>, de <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> que
                        est iuxta <rs key="#Castle">castellare</rs> in loco <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/91"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Castle">Cornino</placeName>, sicut videtur
                        continere per <rs key="#Canals">fossa</rs> ex omni parte et <rs
                            key="#Aqueducts">acqueducto</rs>, ita in Christi nomine dimitto et
                        refuto et rennuo ac concedo suprascripta terra de castellare in manibus <rs
                            key="#Priests">presbiteri</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests #Monks">Giberti</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Priests #Monks">Sesmondi</persName>, <rs key="#Monks">monacis</rs>
                        de <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/78">Sancti
                            Quirici</orgName> sito <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/86">Populonio</placeName>, ad partem
                        et utilitatem ipsius monasterii omni tempore sit in potestate vestra
                        vestrisque successoribus faciendi exinde quicquid facere ad salutem
                        monasterii volueritis. Et si in aliquo tempore ego, qui supra Rogerius, vel
                        mei heredes aliquod de predicta terrra exinde intentionaverimus aut retolli
                        vel subtrai quaesierimus, nos vel ille homo cui nos eam dedissemus aut
                        dederimus per aliquod ingenium, et taciti et pacifici atque quieti
                        persistere non voluerimus et eam ab omni homine defendere non potuerimus et
                        non defensavimus, tunc pro Dei amore et libenti a meo animo obligo me
                        meosque heredes penam composituros in predicto monasterio argenti optimi
                        libras XL in prefinitum, quia sic complacuit animo meo. Pro confirmatione
                            <persName key="#Notary">Petri</persName> domni regis <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarius</rs> scribere rogavi. Actum in loco <placeName>Monte Sancti
                            Laurentii</placeName>, sito Cornino, <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/87"><rs key="#Administrative_units"
                                >territorio</rs> Populoniense.</geogName> Signum manus suprascripti
                        Rogerii quondam Ildebrandi qui hanc cartula refutationis et defensionis
                        fieri rogavi. Signa manuum <persName>Gerardi</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Raineri</persName> de <placeName>Prata</placeName> et
                            <persName>Rufinelli</persName> quondam <persName>Alberti</persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/87">Suvereto</placeName>
                        et <persName>Alferi</persName> quondam *** rogati testes. <persName
                            key="#Notary">Petrus</persName> domini regis <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarius</rs> postradita complevi et dedit. </ab>
